summary:
I study Economics and Business Economics at Maastricht University.  Previously I graduated bilingual High school with International Baccalaureate Diploma. I have developed a passion for economics and geography. My biggest interests are financ,e Forex, international economics, macroeconomics, sustainable development and renewable energy.
I speak fluent English, German and Polish. 
I currently work as a Technical Sales Advisor at Lynk&Co where I have gained experience in accounting, sales, logistics and customer support.
